int in time we have gotten over 40,000 replies and they keep coming in.<br>I don't want EverQuest players to go play DaoC and I myself don't want to, but Verant need to know there are more problem than they want to admit to.<br>I hear lots of good things and lots of bad things about EverQuest but no one has sat down and taken the time to manage a large number of players at one time to let Verant know how many are really having problem.<br>That's the whole reason for this petition, not to get everyone over to DaoC.<br>Please just let your guild members reply to this good or bad and let us get a better idea on how big this problem really is.<br><br>Some stats:<br>Out of 20,000 petitions we have gone through so far 80% will not leave EQ and 70% feel that patches need a bit more testing.<br>The EverQuest play is very loyal to EQ and just wants it to be the best game out there.<br>www.norrathskeepers.net/petition.html  <p>Konk Decaptor Live fast, Run Fast, Live Long, Go LDGuild Leader of Norraths Keepers Of Rdecet</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/ukonkdecaptor.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Konk Decaptor</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0> at: 2/18/02 5:16:48 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=20371A><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bcircleofsisters.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=sneax>Sneax</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Sister</span><br>  Posts: 61<br> <font color=#660000>(2/18/02 3:30:18 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fcircleofsistersfrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=283.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Can Verant Change????</span><hr size=1> I personaly would not get involved in a petition this vague.  A petition needs to